  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Activity
    Contains the content for activity logs for interactions with the app.
    Liquor
    Liquor is used as an object for the inventory to configure to scales.
    Location
    Location reflects a business.
    RestResponse
    Data transfer object using in REST responses containing a signal for the Arduino to change the light switch with reflecting the status, and a message used for debugging purposed.
    Scale
    Scale model is used to emmulate the actual Arduino Scale on site.
    User
    User Class with informative attributes to distinguish users from each other and validate their accounts.
